quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  20,25,"Moosa ne arz kiya “ parwardigar, mera seena khol de"
  20,26,Aur mere kaam ko mere liye aasaan karde
  20,27,Aur meri zubaan ki girah suljha de
  20,28,Taa-ke log meri baat samajh sakein
  20,29,Aur mere liye mere apne kumbe (my own family) se ek wazir muqarrar karde
  20,30,"Haroon, jo mera bhai hai"
  20,31,Uske zariye se mera haath mazboot kar
  20,32,Aur usko mere kaam mein shareek karde
  20,33,Hum khoob teri paaki bayan karein
  20,34,Aur khoob tera charcha karein
  20,35,Tu hamesha hamare haal par nigraan raha hai”
  20,36,Farmaya “ diya gaya jo tu nay maanga aey Moosa
  20,37,Humne phir ek martaba tujhpar ehsan kiya
  20,38,"Yaad karo woh waqt jabke humne teri Maa ko ishara kiya, aisa ishara jo wahee ke zariye kiya jaata hai"
  20,39,"Ke is bacchey ko sandook (box) mein rakh de aur sandook ko dariya mein chodh de, dariya isey saahil par phenk dega aur isey mera dushman aur is bacchey ka dushman utha lega. Maine apni taraf se tujhpar mohabbat taari kardi aur aisa intizam kiya ke tu meri nigrani mein paala jaye"
  20,40,"Yaad kar jabke teri behan chal rahi thi, phir jaa kar kehti hai, “main tumhein uska pata doon jo is bacchey ki parwarish acchi tarah karey?” Is tarah humne tujhey phir teri Maa ke paas pahuncha diya taa-ke uski aankh thandi rahey aur woh ranjeeda na ho. Aur (yeh bhi yaad kar ke) tu nay ek shaks ko qatal kardiya tha, humne tujhey is phanday se nikala aur tujhey mukhtalif aazmaaishon se guzara aur tu Madiyan ke logon mein kai saal thehra raha. Phir ab theek apne waqt par tu aa gaya hai aey Moosa"
  20,41,Maine tujhey apne kaam ka bana liya hai
  20,42,"Ja, tu aur tera bhai meri nishaniyon ke saath, aur dekho tum meri yaad mein taqseer (susti /negligence) na karna"
  20,43,Jao tum dono Firoun ke paas ke woh sarkash ho gaya hai
  20,44,"Ussey narmi ke saath baat karna, shayad ke woh naseehat qabool karey ya darr jaaye”"
  20,45,"Dono ne arz kiya “ parwardigar, humein andesha hai ke woh humpar zyadati karega ya pil padega(treat us cruelly)”"
  20,46,"Farmaya” daro mat, main tumhare saath hoon, sab kuch sun raha hoon aur dekh raha hoon"
  20,47,"Jao uske paas aur kaho ke hum tere Rubb ke faristaade (messengers) hain, bani Israel ko hamare saath janey ke liye chodh de aur unko takleef na de. Hum tere paas tere Rubb ki nishani lekar aaye hain aur salamati hai uske liye jo raah-e-raast ki pairwi karey"
  20,48,Humko wahee (revelation) se bataya gaya hai ke azaab hai uske liye jo jhutlaye aur mooh moadey.”
  20,49,"Firoun ne kaha “accha, to phir tum dono ka Rubb kaun hai aey Moosa?”"
  20,50,"Moosa ne jawab diya “hamara Rubb woh hai jisne har cheez ko uski saakht bakshi(given distinctive form), phir usko raasta bataya”"
  20,51,Firoun bola “aur pehle jo nasalein (generations) guzar chuki hain unki phir kya halat thi?”
  20,52,"Moosa ne kaha “uska ilam mere Rubb ke paas ek nawishte (record) mein mehfooz hai, mera Rub na chukta hai na bhoolta hai”"
  20,53,"Wahi jisne tumhare liye zameen ka farsh bichaya, aur usmein tumhare chalne ko raaste banaye, aur upar se pani barsaya, phir uske zariye se mukhtalif aqsam ki paidawaar nikali"
  20,54,"Khao aur apne jaanwaron ko bhi charao, yaqeenan is mein bahut si nishaniyan hain aqal rakhne walon ke liye"